Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.48,0:00:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，接下来我们要做的事情是创建一个数据模型
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.76,0:00:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这个数据模型叫做 Sound
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.63,0:00:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,它会有一个声音文件和图像文件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.92,0:00:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,并且有一个叫 Category（类别）的变量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.14,0:00:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们将创建一个声音管理器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.44,0:00:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我们就能得到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.09,0:00:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,一个获取所有声音的接口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.53,0:00:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,或者是按照类别获取声音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.99,0:00:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,所以其实我们会传递一个空的或已经填充数据的 ObservableCollection
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.14,0:00:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将与它绑定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.82,0:00:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,往里面装 Sound 的实例
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.24,0:00:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,装入全部的 Sound，或者特定类别的，根据需要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.99,0:00:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我要做一些首要的绑定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.38,0:00:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我们就能在屏幕上看到一些东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.41,0:00:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,它并没有什么实质的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.87,0:00:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但它会让我们很容易上手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.14,0:00:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们现在就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.81,0:00:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,创建一个 Model 目录
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.48,0:01:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,然后在里面创建一个类
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,叫做 Sound
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,在这个类里面我要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.33,0:01:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,创建一个 Name 属性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.86,0:01:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 Category
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.17,0:01:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,待会再来确定这里的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.44,0:01:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我要在这里加入一个枚举类型
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.15,0:01:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,然后再来一个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.26,0:01:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,AudioFile
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.79,0:01:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 ImageFile
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.35,0:01:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我要创建一个 SoundCategory 枚举
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.26,0:01:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,public enum SoundCategory.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.39,0:01:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,然后这些 Category 枚举值是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.61,0:01:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.31,0:01:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就是 Animals, Cartoons 这些
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.26,0:01:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Taunts, Warnings 之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.44,0:01:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.68,0:01:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Cartoons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.50,0:01:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Taunts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.03,0:01:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Warnings好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,然后把这个 Category 属性变成 SoundCategory 类型的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.13,0:02:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好的我觉得我接下来还要做些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,来方便我们填充数据
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道AudioFile和ImageFile遵循一个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.67,0:02:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,相似的模式，他们都会是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,/Assets/Audio/<类别名>/<声音名>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这些图标也是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.97,0:02:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,它们都是 /Assets/Images/Animals
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.77,0:02:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,或者是把 Animals 替换成 <类别名>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我可以让我创建这些新的小家伙们（实例）变得更加简单
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,只要重载一个构造器（构造函数/构造方法）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 public Sound，参数是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Name 还有 Category, SoundCategory
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:03:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们可以这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.21,0:03:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Name = name
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.17,0:03:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Category = category
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.89,0:03:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,AudioFile = String.Format……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会给它一个Category和Name
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.44,0:03:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这里面应该是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.42,0:03:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,/Assets/Audio/
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,类别名，斜线，名称，.wav
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,0:03:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们可以在Image这里做同样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,ImageFile.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,只要把这个 Audio 改成 Images
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.27,0:03:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,把 wav 改成 png
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把这两个属性的赋值封装了，让创建实例变得非常简单
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.07,0:04:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我来确认一下我把这些玩意儿的名字都写对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.43,0:04:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,比如这些文件夹...嗯看起来不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧我觉得我们现在目前为止很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,下一步，创建一个声音管理器类
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这可以让我们获得 Sound 的实例
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,所以...（这个类叫 SoundManager）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢让这些管理类静态（static）、无状态
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,或者说让这里面的方法是静态方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我想做的是应该能向它传递一个 ObservableCollection，然后填充数据
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我知道我应该创建一个 private static
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.62,0:04:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,然后它会返回
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,返回个啥？...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.63,0:04:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯它会返回一个List<Sound>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们叫它 getSounds
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们创建一个变量 sounds
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,new 一个 List<Sound> 给它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们调用 sounds.Add
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.99,0:05:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,加一个 new Sound，并使用我们刚刚为构造器建立的那个重载
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,给它一个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,比如说 Cow
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,还有...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只需要遵循这个模式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.84,0:05:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,重复几次一样的事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,然后返回这个 sounds
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，还有，其他的比如 Cat
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.90,0:05:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,然后这里，我得看下我的文件夹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:06:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Cartoons 里面有 Gun 和 Spring
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Gun、Spring，这些都属于 Cartoons
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.02,0:06:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好的.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.98,0:06:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是Taunts: Clock 和 LOL, 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.38,0:06:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,最后, Warnings: Ship 和 Siren.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,呃呃呃 Warnings, 好的.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.72,0:06:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,目前为止很不错.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,可以获得一个 List<Sound>，所以 public static void GetAllSounds
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,public static void GetAllSounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,然后首先我要做的事情是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:07:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,var sounds = getSounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,然后传入一个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,OberservableCollection<Sound>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,因为那是我们将要从Main.xaml.cs传入的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.72,0:07:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,ObservableCollection<Sound>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,让我获取那个命名空间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,System.Collections.ObjectModel, 没错.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哦我应该给参数一个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道给它起个什么名字好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,sounds, 这里我就用这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这个就命名成 allSounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,很难决定怎么去取名,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.20,0:07:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直这么说，但确实是真的.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧, all sounds, 很好.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 sounds.Clear() 因为我想去除
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,传入集合已经有的东西.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你还记得我们做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.24,0:08:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,有趣的 lambda 表达式吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.24,0:08:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得可以那么做，应该有效果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.49,0:08:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯我觉得应该可以.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.07,0:08:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好的我们测试一下确保它是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但我确实觉得应该用 lambda 表达式就是它了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.38,0:08:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我们将遍历所有从 getSounds 得到的 Sound
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.74,0:08:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,对于每一个我都要把它加进这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,叫做 sounds 的 ObservableCollection<Sound>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.31,0:08:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要返回任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,因为它是通过引用传递的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这里我们也做同样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.64,0:08:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,它俩没啥区别
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.39,0:08:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们依然有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.11,0:08:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这个 ObservableCollection<Sound> sounds
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:09:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,它会作为参数传入，同时我还想传入
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,一个叫做 soundCategory 的参数
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.53,0:09:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们根据 soundCategory 过滤结果
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这个我改一下...好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,所以这里我们一样让 allSounds = getSounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这一次我需要筛选了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 var filteredSounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,（见代码）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,然后用 sounds.Clear()
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.11,0:09:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就像之前那样, 然后,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.01,0:09:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,filteredSounds.ForEach.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？为什么没法那么做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:09:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我并没有把这个转换成 List
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.69,0:10:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,filteredSounds.ForEach
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,给一个 p
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.01,0:10:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,调用 sounds.Add 添加那个对象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.28,0:10:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,到我们的 ObservableCollection<Sound> 里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我们需要为 SoundManager 和 Sound 做的所有准备，至少现在看来够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,现在在 MainPage.xaml.cs,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将要创建一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.28,0:10:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,私有的引用关联到 ObservableCollection
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.35,0:10:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,叫sounds的动态数据集
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,啊, ObservableCollection<Sound>！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 x 2
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好，没问题.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:11:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，非常好.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来我想做的是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,首先，当我们初始化好这些部件时.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们调用 SoundManager,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.51,0:11:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,得到所有的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是 ObservableCollection<Sound>
