Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.29,0:12:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我将设置源
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.25,0:12:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Source=x:Bind, 然后是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.96,0:12:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,名字是什么来着, AudioFile?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.09,0:12:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来对吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得应该是对的.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,哦抱歉 ImageFile 而不是 AudioFile.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好现在行了.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.77,0:12:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来看看这部分做了什么.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哦我需要给他一个源, 所以,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,ItemsSource,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:13:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我会用 x:Bind 和 Sounds绑定.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.42,0:13:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,现在来两手交叉，托住下巴，满怀希望，等待
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们至少会看到一些图片...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没有引用，让我修了它
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.39,0:13:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，好.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，这并不漂亮,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.55,0:13:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但这里已经有了所有的图标了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，这些是挺丑的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.54,0:13:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但我的绑定已经生效了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.44,0:13:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来我们调整一下，快速看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么会有这种奇怪的事情发生对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为基本的问题出在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:14:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,, SplitView 应该设置成 Grid.Row="1".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得这就是最大的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.33,0:14:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,所以让我们再试一遍吧，这至少可以让那个灰色小区域再降一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，没有什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这里我在想...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们继续然后...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,搞定汉堡按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们写 MySplitView.IsOpen
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,MySplitView.IsOpen = !MySplitView.IsPaneOpen
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.89,0:14:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,MySplitView.IsOpen = !MySplitView.IsPaneOpen
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样，至少它会打开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我要做的另一件事是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.46,0:14:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要另一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要另一个方案
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.03,0:14:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,除了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.59,0:15:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,SplitView 的面板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.03,0:15:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我要用个 ListView 来代替它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.53,0:15:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我要新造一个模型类
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,一个叫做 MenuItem 的新的视图模型
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们继续快点搞定他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.29,0:15:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,非常简单
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只需要一到两分钟就能完成它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,所以现在我们来处理MenuItem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,写一个public class MenuItem,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.00,0:15:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,然后写个...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,IconFile, 然后是 SoundCategory,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.70,0:15:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这记录这个图标代表哪个类别
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这会帮我们筛选
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,在 SplitView 里根据选择的菜单条目来筛选声音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,现在回到这个 MainPage.xaml
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.04,0:15:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要做的是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里搞点事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.68,0:16:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我要创建一个私有的 List<MenuItem>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,叫做MenuItems.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们会设置这个...设置这个类型为
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.28,0:16:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,, SoundCategory.Animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 IconFile 的路径在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Assets/Icons/animals.png
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.56,0:16:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Assets/Icons/animals.png, 嗯没错.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.16,0:16:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们继续
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.55,0:16:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,换上 cartoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.59,0:17:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 taunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,, cartoons.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.73,0:17:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Taunts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Warnings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们把这些绑定到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.80,0:17:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的 ListView
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.23,0:17:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们继续...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.30,0:17:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们要添加一个 StackPanel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,加上 Orientation="Horizontal".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这里我们添加一个图片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.99,0:18:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,然后设置它的路径
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.95,0:18:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,让他等于 IconFile.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.39,0:18:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我想应该设置
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.93,0:18:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Height="0.5", Width="45".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.19,0:18:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能要减小一点，但是我们先这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.69,0:18:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,然后就是旁边的TextBlock，这里面会有文字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.37,0:18:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,酱紫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.93,0:18:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,FontSize="18".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我知道我左边需要一点内边距
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不过还是在左边加点外边距吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"10,0,0,0".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.72,0:18:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,然后在这个 ListView 我要设置一下源
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.39,0:19:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,（见代码）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，我们来看看有没有用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.88,0:19:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,也许看起来不好看，但我们先确保它工作正常
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.26,0:19:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我哪里有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,MenuItems不能被搜寻到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,IconFile, Category, 等等，啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.95,0:19:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,MenuItems.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,哦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.99,0:19:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,LIstView需要一个模板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我真有点提前庆祝胜利了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.36,0:19:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们写上x:DataType="data:MenuItem".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.81,0:19:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,x:DataType="data:MenuItem".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.87,0:19:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这样应该没问题了，我们生成他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.69,0:20:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这次又是什么问题。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，和之前同样的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,MenuItems = new List<MenuItem>.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.84,0:20:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,走你.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是我想要的呢。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我哪里弄错了。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里错了啊。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:21:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，我觉得我肯定是混乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.77,0:21:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这样看他怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,走你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.31,0:21:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，现在所有外边距有点问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但很容易搞定的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我会在下个视频搞定它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这个视频已经够长的了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，所以我们创建了两个数据源
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.08,0:21:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,一个是给菜单的，但主要的是给声音的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.65,0:21:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,同时我们也创建了 SoundManager
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.81,0:21:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们能够获取那些声音并通过类别筛选他们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.16,0:21:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,下期视频我们会真正地把声音和媒体文件相连接
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.96,0:21:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,然后开始播放他们，令人激动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好那我们下个课程再见，谢谢
